ğŸ“Š Key KPIs

This dashboard includes the following KPIs:

Total Transactions: 500

Total Sales: $174,254.79

Total Profit Estimate: $40,274.95

Average Rating: 6.92

KPI cards were created using PivotTables and custom formatting.

