ğŸ” Feature Engineering

New calculated fields were added to enhance analysis:

RevenueWithoutTax

DayOfWeek

MonthName

HourOfDay

ProfitEstimate (30% margin)

These features improve trend and profitability insights.

ğŸ“Š Key Insights
1. Sales Performance

The supermarket generated $174k in total revenue across 500 transactions.

Estimated profit is ~$40k, assuming a 30% margin.

2. Top Product Lines

Electronic Accessories and Food & Beverages lead in total sales.

Baby Care and Fashion Accessories contribute less revenue.

3. Branch Performance

Branch A and Branch C outperform Branch B.

Branch B shows growth potential.

4. Customer Trends

Monthly sales remain steady with small fluctuations.

Average customer rating is 6.92, indicating moderate satisfaction.

5. Payment Insights

Ewallet is the most popular payment method.

Digital payment adoption is strong across customers.

6. Gender & Customer Type

Sales are balanced between Male and Female customers.

Members slightly outperform Normal customers in total spending.

ğŸ“„ Conclusion

This dashboard provides a clear and interactive overview of supermarket sales activity.
It highlights high-performing regions, products, and customer trends, enabling data-driven decisions for inventory, promotions, and customer engagement.


